---
// Single-file academic data-journalism redesign — dark theme + SVG sub-figures
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Module Control in Youth Symptom Networks — Companion Site</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Companion site for the manuscript: Module control in youth symptom networks across COVID-19" />
  <style is:inline>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap');

    :root {
      --bg: #0D1B2A;
      --card: #162236;
      --accent: #F5A623;
      --text: #E8EDF2;
      --muted: #4A6080;
      --border: #1E3048;
      --footer-bg: #080F17;
      --str: #CC79A7;
      --emo: #E69F00;
      --csf: #56B4E9;
      --spf: #009E73;
      --phy: #9EA33A;
      --radius: 10px;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.72;
      font-size: 16px;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    h1, h2, h3, h4 { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2; }
    a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
    button { font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; }

    .wrap { width: min(1080px, calc(100vw - 48px)); margin: 0 auto; }
    .sec-label { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .sec-title { font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.2vw, 2.4rem); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .sec-sub { color: var(--muted); font-size: clamp(0.92rem, 1vw, 1.02rem); max-width: 60ch; line-height: 1.7; }

    /* ── Nav ── */
    .site-nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; background: rgba(13,27,42,0.85); backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(180%); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(180%); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .nav-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 12px 0; }
    .nav-brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.88rem; }
    .nav-mark { width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 7px; background: var(--accent); display: grid; place-items: center; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--bg); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 4px; }
    .nav-link { padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 6px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.84rem; font-weight: 400; transition: all 0.2s; text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-link:hover, .nav-link.active { color: var(--text); background: rgba(245,166,35,0.08); text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-link.active { color: var(--accent); }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center; padding: 80px 24px 40px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -40%; left: -20%; width: 140%; height: 140%; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%, rgba(245,166,35,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%); pointer-events: none; }
    .hero-overline { font-size: 0.76rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.22em; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 28px; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.2s forwards; }
    .hero-title { font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5rem); line-height: 1.06; margin-bottom: 28px; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.4s forwards; }
    .hero-title .amber { color: var(--accent); }
    .hero-sub { font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.2vw, 1.12rem); color: var(--muted); max-width: 56ch; margin-bottom: 48px; line-height: 1.72; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.6s forwards; }
    .hero-stats { display: flex; gap: clamp(24px, 5vw, 56px); margin-bottom: 48px; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.8s forwards; }
    .h-stat { text-align: center; }
    .h-stat-num { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.6rem); line-height: 1.1; }
    .h-stat-label { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 6px; }
    .hero-domains { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 48px; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 1.0s forwards; }
    .hdot { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); }
    .hdot i { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; }
    .scroll-arrow { position: absolute; bottom: 32px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 1.2s forwards; }
    .scroll-arrow span { display: block; width: 20px; height: 20px; border-right: 2px solid var(--muted); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--muted); transform: rotate(45deg); animation: bounce 2s infinite; }
    @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    @keyframes bounce { 0%,100% { transform: rotate(45deg) translateY(0); } 50% { transform: rotate(45deg) translateY(8px); } }

    /* ── Shared figures ── */
    .fig-wrap { border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card); }
    .fig-wrap img { width: 100%; display: block; }
    .fig-cap { padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 0.76rem; color: var(--muted); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
    /* SVG figures need light bg */
    .svg-fig { border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: #f8f9fb; padding: 8px; }
    .svg-fig img { width: 100%; display: block; border-radius: 6px; }
    .svg-fig .fig-cap { background: var(--card); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 8px -8px -8px; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 0; }

    /* ── Cards ── */
    .s-card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 28px); position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s; }
    .s-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
    .s-card-num { position: absolute; top: -8px; right: 12px; font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 4rem; color: var(--accent); opacity: 0.07; line-height: 1; pointer-events: none; }
    .s-card h4 { font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.1vw, 1.12rem); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .s-card p { font-size: clamp(0.86rem, 0.92vw, 0.94rem); color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }

    /* ── Grid layouts ── */
    .g2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }
    .g3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 14px; }
    .g12 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(16px, 3vw, 32px); align-items: start; }

    /* ── Sections ── */
    .sec { padding: clamp(60px, 8vw, 100px) 0; }

    /* ── Phase timeline ── */
    .timeline { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; position: relative; margin: 36px 0 32px; padding: 0 20px; }
    .timeline::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 20px; right: 20px; height: 2px; background: var(--border); transform: translateY(-50%); }
    .tl-node { position: relative; z-index: 1; background: none; border: 2px solid var(--muted); width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500; }
    .tl-node.active { background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--bg); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(245,166,35,0.25); }
    .tl-node:hover:not(.active) { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
    .tl-label { position: absolute; top: calc(100% + 8px); white-space: nowrap; font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); transition: color 0.3s; }
    .tl-node.active .tl-label { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; }
    .tl-date { position: absolute; bottom: calc(100% + 6px); white-space: nowrap; font-size: 0.64rem; color: var(--muted); opacity: 0.6; }

    .info-panel { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: clamp(18px, 2.5vw, 28px); }
    .pill-tag { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--accent); padding: 4px 10px; border: 1px solid rgba(245,166,35,0.25); border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .p-badge { font-size: 0.74rem; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(245,166,35,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(245,166,35,0.15); color: var(--muted); display: inline-block; margin-right: 6px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .p-badge strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
    .sc-box { background: rgba(13,27,42,0.6); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 16px; }
    .sc-box h5 { font-size: 0.76rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
    .sc-box p { font-size: 0.86rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.55; }
    .phase-fig-transition { transition: opacity 0.4s ease; }
    .phase-fig-transition.fading { opacity: 0.3; }
    .svg-box { border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card); }

    /* ── Backbone ── */
    .bb-pill { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 999px; padding: 10px 18px; font-size: 0.86rem; color: var(--muted); text-align: left; transition: all 0.25s; }
    .bb-pill:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--text); }
    .bb-pill.active { background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--bg); font-weight: 500; }
    .bb-detail { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: clamp(18px, 2.5vw, 28px); min-height: 180px; }
    .bb-tag { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 999px; border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--muted); margin-right: 6px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .bb-detail h4 { font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.2vw, 1.2rem); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .bb-detail p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .bb-detail p strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
    .macro-card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: clamp(16px, 2vw, 22px); display: flex; gap: 12px; transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s; }
    .macro-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
    .macro-icon { width: 4px; border-radius: 2px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .macro-card h5 { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .macro-card p { font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.55; }

    /* ── Methods ── */
    .pipeline { position: relative; padding-left: 28px; }
    .pipeline::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 15px; top: 22px; bottom: 22px; width: 2px; background: var(--border); }
    .pipe-step { display: flex; gap: 16px; padding: 14px 0; position: relative; }
    .pipe-num { width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); display: grid; place-items: center; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--bg); flex-shrink: 0; position: relative; z-index: 1; margin-left: -28px; }
    .pipe-step h5 { font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .pipe-step p { font-size: 0.86rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ── Robustness bars ── */
    .rob-panel { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: clamp(18px, 2.5vw, 26px); }
    .rob-panel h4 { font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.1vw, 1.1rem); margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .rob-sub { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .rob-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 68px 1fr 52px; gap: 10px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .rob-label { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; }
    .rob-track { height: 10px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(30,48,72,0.6); overflow: hidden; }
    .rob-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 999px; width: 0; transition: width 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1); }
    .rob-fill.green { background: var(--spf); } .rob-fill.yellow { background: var(--accent); } .rob-fill.red { background: var(--str); }
    .rob-val { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 500; text-align: right; }
    .rob-val.green { color: var(--spf); } .rob-val.yellow { color: var(--accent); } .rob-val.red { color: var(--str); }
    .rob-note { font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 14px; line-height: 1.55; }
    .ev-card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: clamp(14px, 1.5vw, 18px); transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s; }
    .ev-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
    .ev-card h5 { font-size: 0.84rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .ev-card p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.55; }

    /* ── Significance ── */
    .sig-card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 28px); border-top: 3px solid var(--accent); transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s; }
    .sig-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
    .sig-card:nth-child(1) { border-top-color: var(--spf); }
    .sig-card:nth-child(2) { border-top-color: var(--csf); }
    .sig-card:nth-child(3) { border-top-color: var(--emo); }
    .sig-cat { font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.16em; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .sig-card:nth-child(1) .sig-cat { color: var(--spf); }
    .sig-card:nth-child(2) .sig-cat { color: var(--csf); }
    .sig-card:nth-child(3) .sig-cat { color: var(--emo); }
    .sig-card h4 { font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.1vw, 1.12rem); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .sig-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }

    /* ── Accordion ── */
    .accord-item { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); margin-bottom: 8px; overflow: hidden; background: var(--card); }
    .accord-trigger { width: 100%; background: none; border: none; padding: 16px 20px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; color: var(--text); font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 500; text-align: left; transition: color 0.2s; }
    .accord-trigger:hover { color: var(--accent); }
    .accord-icon { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--muted); transition: transform 0.3s; font-style: normal; }
    .accord-item.open .accord-icon { transform: rotate(45deg); }
    .accord-body { max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.4s ease; }
    .accord-item.open .accord-body { max-height: 300px; }
    .accord-content { padding: 0 20px 18px; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    .site-footer { background: var(--footer-bg); padding: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px) 0 40px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .footer-label { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .gl-entry { background: rgba(22,34,54,0.5); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 18px; }
    .gl-entry dt { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 0.96rem; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .gl-entry dt .tag { font-size: 0.64rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--muted); background: rgba(74,96,128,0.2); padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 4px; margin-left: 6px; vertical-align: middle; }
    .gl-entry dd { font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.55; }
    .res-btn { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; padding: 16px 24px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; flex: 1; min-width: 180px; transition: all 0.25s; }
    .res-btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); text-decoration: none; }
    .res-btn-icon { width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 8px; background: rgba(245,166,35,0.1); display: grid; place-items: center; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--accent); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .res-btn-text span { display: block; font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); }
    .citation { font-size: 0.76rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 24px; max-width: 60ch; font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', monospace; }

    /* ── Scroll reveal ── */
    .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease; }
    .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .stagger > * { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease; }
    .stagger.visible > *:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0s; opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .stagger.visible > *:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.08s; opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .stagger.visible > *:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 0.12s; opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .stagger.visible > *:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: 0.18s; opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .stagger.visible > *:nth-child(5) { transition-delay: 0.24s; opacity: 1; transform: none; }

    /* ── Utility ── */
    .mt16 { margin-top: 16px; } .mt24 { margin-top: 24px; } .mt36 { margin-top: 36px; }
    .gap8 { gap: 8px; } .gap12 { gap: 12px; } .gap16 { gap: 16px; }
    .flex-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hero-stats { gap: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
      .g2, .g12 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .g3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .timeline { overflow-x: auto; justify-content: flex-start; padding-bottom: 32px; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch; }
      .timeline::before { display: none; }
      .tl-node { flex-shrink: 0; margin: 0 16px; }
      .wrap { width: calc(100vw - 32px); }
      .bb-pills-row { flex-direction: row !important; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav class="site-nav">
  <div class="wrap nav-inner">
    <a href="#" class="nav-brand"><span class="nav-mark">MC</span> Fan &amp; Zhang · Nanjing Medical Univ.</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a class="nav-link" href="#summary">Summary</a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="#phases">Phases</a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="#backbone">Backbone</a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="#methods">Methods</a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="#robustness">Robustness</a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="#significance">Significance</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- 1 HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-overline">Editorial &amp; Reviewer Companion</div>
  <h1 class="hero-title">Same scaffold,<br/><span class="amber">different controllers.</span></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Across five phases of the COVID-19 pandemic, youth symptom networks preserved a broadly similar modular architecture while the distribution of control shifted from an early stress-centered configuration toward a later cross-domain pattern.</p>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="h-stat"><div class="h-stat-num" data-target="14181">0</div><div class="h-stat-label">U.S. young adults</div></div>
    <div class="h-stat"><div class="h-stat-num" data-target="47">0</div><div class="h-stat-label">MHQ symptoms</div></div>
    <div class="h-stat"><div class="h-stat-num" data-target="5">0</div><div class="h-stat-label">Pandemic phases</div></div>
    <div class="h-stat"><div class="h-stat-num" data-target="4">0</div><div class="h-stat-label">Symptom domains</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-domains">
    <span class="hdot"><i style="background:var(--str)"></i> Stress Response</span>
    <span class="hdot"><i style="background:var(--emo)"></i> Emotional Regulation</span>
    <span class="hdot"><i style="background:var(--csf)"></i> Cognitive &amp; Social</span>
    <span class="hdot"><i style="background:var(--spf)"></i> Self-perception &amp; Physiological</span>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-arrow"><span></span></div>
</section>

<!-- 2 SUMMARY -->
<section id="summary" class="sec">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="reveal"><div class="sec-label">30-Second Summary</div><h2 class="sec-title">Four signals that define this paper.</h2></div>
    <div class="g2 stagger mt36">
      <div class="s-card reveal"><span class="s-card-num">01</span><h4>Question</h4><p>Did the pandemic reorganize the architecture of youth symptoms, or mainly reallocate control within a conserved scaffold?</p></div>
      <div class="s-card reveal"><span class="s-card-num">02</span><h4>Evidence</h4><p>Repeated cross-sections of U.S. young adults aged 18–24 across five pandemic phases, with 47 MHQ items and an India replication cohort.</p></div>
